Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不准叫我金槍魚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:23:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  冷靜應戰吧
